events.text: The Celtics traded Carlos Clark, Scott Wedman, a 1985 1st round pick (BOS), and a 1987 2nd round pick (BOS) to the Cavaliers for World B. Free.
The Cavaliers released Campy Russell.
The Bucks traded Craig Hodges, a 1985 1st round pick (MIL), a 1985 2nd round pick (MIL), and a 1987 1st round pick (MIL) to the SuperSonics for Tom Chambers.
The SuperSonics traded Frank Brickowski to the Knicks for Truck Robinson, a 1985 2nd round pick (NYK), and a 1987 2nd round pick (NYK).

The Celtics traded Greg Kite, Cedric Maxwell, a 1986 2nd round pick (BOS), and a 1988 1st round pick (BOS) to the Mavericks for Kurt Nimphius, Dale Ellis, Derek Harper, and a 1988 2nd round pick (DAL).
The Nuggets traded Willie White, Elston Turner, and a 1985 1st round pick (DEN) to the Mavericks for Brad Davis.
